title: DOUBLE FEATURE HELL 3 (it's a jungle out there)

sources.title: DoubleFratureHell3itsAJungleOutThere
sources.description: The adventure begins with coming attractions and a cartoon, followed by the first feature, "Law of the Jungle." The intermission featurette is chapter 11 of the serial, "Jungle Girl," followed by the second feature, "Forbidden Jungle." Vaccinations are not required for this safari. Flea powder is recommended for balcony seating. NOTE: The complete "Jungle Girl" serial is available on DVD from VCI Entertainment. All the other items in this simulation are found in various IA collections.
